in Las Vegas, has a new trainer -- Don Turner. 
</P>
<P>
 Holyfield and Emanuel Steward couldn't come to terms.Steward wanted $400,000 
and Holyfield offered $300,000. Turner once worked for Steward. Jurisprudence 
</P>
<P>
 Dave Stewart criticized police in the Tampa suburb of Dunedin, Fla., for their 
handling of a nightclub argument that led to the arrests of the Toronto Blue 
Jays pitcher and teammate Todd Stottlemyre. 
