league titles and finished fifth at the Southern Section individual 
championships last year. Donovan and Henderson are just a few strokes behind, 
and Safallo said Lucidi is not too far behind that. Safallo is bullish. "They 
seem to want it and they work at it," Safallo said. "I have a lot of guys here 
that are putting a lot of time in. It will be a long time before we have 
