</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
THANKS FOR GENEROSITY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 On behalf of the children and families served by the Public Social Services 
Agency, Protective Services Division, CAAN (Child Abuse And Neglect) and the 
Children's Services Auxiliary, I would like to commend the generosity and 
concern of the individuals, organizations and county employees who supported 
our holiday toy and gift program. 
</P>
<P>
 Each year, our organizations give toys and gifts to children who are in foster 
care or at risk of abuse or neglect in their own homes.This year, more than 400 
social workers, foster parents and biological families "shopped" at our special 
toy store. Nearly 2,000 children received at least three gifts each this 
holiday season. 
</P>
<P>
 Diana G. Caskey 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura 
</P>
<P>
 Dianna Caskey is a foster home recruitment specialist in Ventura County's 
Public Social Services Agency.  
