ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: LOS ALAMITOS; JANITORIAL SERVICES CONTRACT AWARDED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BERT ELJERA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The City Council last week picked Commercial Building Co. over seven other 
contractors to provide janitorial services to City Hall and other city 
buildings. 
</P>
<P>
 The Santa Ana-based company's winning bid of $15,000 a year was $8,000 lower 
