said. 
</P>
<P>
 In addition to City Hall, the janitorial firm will clean the council chambers, 
finance and engineering offices, the youth and community centers and restrooms 
at Laurel Park. 
</P>
<P>
 Six other companies submitted bids for the contract in November, according to 
Public Services Director M. Victor Rollinger. BERT ELJERA 
