<TEXT>
<P>
 Wrigley Field -- A photograph that ran in some editions of Monday's Times was 
incorrectly identified as Los Angeles' Wrigley Field in 1954. In fact, it was 
an artist's rendition of a proposed expansion of the stadium that was never 
completed. 
</P>
