<TEXT>
<P>
 Film credits -- A story on Film-forum's "Scratching the Belly of the Beast" 
festival in the Feb. 12 Calendar section named the wrong filmmakers for two 
films. "Salome" is by Alla Navimova and "The Works 2: Reynar Banham & Mike 
Davis" is by Bruce Yonemoto, Ed de la Torre and Melissa Totten. 
</P>
